                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 11.651,
                                "byte_start": 76800,
                                "byte_stop": 123507,
                                "text": "The disposition of number 72-593, Central Tablet Company against The United States will be announced by Mr. Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 11.651,
                        "stop": 151.218,
                        "byte_start": 123507,
                        "byte_stop": 681691,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15045,
                            "name": "Harry A. Blackmun",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/harry_a_blackmun",
                            "last_name": "Blackmun",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2689,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 13755600,
                                    "date_end": 775890000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2689"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32712,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 50281,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/harry_a_blackmun.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8821,
                            "identifier": "harry_a_blackmun"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 11.651,
                                "stop": 19.014,
                                "byte_start": 123507,
                                "byte_stop": 152869,
                                "text": "Well this is an income tax case coming to us from the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 19.014,
                                "stop": 44.213,
                                "byte_start": 152869,
                                "byte_stop": 253701,
                                "text": "Section 337 of the Federal Internal Revenue Code, provides that gain or loss to a corporation from a sale or exchange of property taking place during a twelve months period, following the corporation\u2019s adoption of a plan of complete liquidation, is not to be recognized or in other words, is tax free to the corporation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 44.213,
                                "stop": 52.287,
                                "byte_start": 253701,
                                "byte_stop": 285989,
                                "text": "What happened here is that a fire largely destroyed the tax payer corporation\u2019s plant in Ohio."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 52.287,
                                "stop": 57.006,
                                "byte_start": 285989,
                                "byte_stop": 304901,
                                "text": "After the fire the corporation adopted a plan of liquidation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 57.006,
                                "stop": 65.806,
                                "byte_start": 304901,
                                "byte_stop": 340114,
                                "text": "There were extensive negotiations with the insurance companies that had provided the fire and business interruption insurance protection."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 65.806,
                                "stop": 71.778,
                                "byte_start": 340114,
                                "byte_stop": 363938,
                                "text": "These loss claims were settled after the adoption of the plan of liquidation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 71.778,
                                "stop": 82.393,
                                "byte_start": 363938,
                                "byte_stop": 406465,
                                "text": "Thus chronologically we have the fire and then the adoption of the plan and during the ensuing year payment of the insurance proceeds."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 82.393,
                                "stop": 88.437,
                                "byte_start": 406465,
                                "byte_stop": 430602,
                                "text": "The proceeds exceeded the corporation\u2019s adjusted income tax basis and the destroyed property."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 88.437,
                                "stop": 103.399,
                                "byte_start": 430602,
                                "byte_stop": 490475,
                                "text": "As a consequence there was gain, and the issue is whether that gain is to be allocated to a happening of a fire or to the settlement of the insurance claims during the year of following the adoption of the plan."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 103.399,
                                "stop": 113.063,
                                "byte_start": 490475,
                                "byte_stop": 529136,
                                "text": "If the former, the gain is taxable to corporation, if the latter the gain under the statute is not recognized or taxed to the corporation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 113.063,
                                "stop": 120.735,
                                "byte_start": 529136,
                                "byte_stop": 559752,
                                "text": "The District Court followed a decision of a few years ago by the Eighth Circuit and entered judgment for the tax payer."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 120.735,
                                "stop": 126.633,
                                "byte_start": 559752,
                                "byte_stop": 583367,
                                "text": "The Court of Appeals refused to follow the Eighth Circuit Opinion and reversed."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 126.633,
                                "stop": 129.261,
                                "byte_start": 583367,
                                "byte_stop": 593920,
                                "text": "We affirm the Court of Appeals."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 129.261,
                                "stop": 134.486,
                                "byte_start": 593920,
                                "byte_stop": 614818,
                                "text": "In an opinion filed today, we have endeavored to trace the history and purpose of the statute."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 134.486,
                                "stop": 138.944,
                                "byte_start": 614818,
                                "byte_stop": 632581,
                                "text": "We have set forth our reasons for reaching our conclusion."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 138.944,
                                "stop": 151.218,
                                "byte_start": 632581,
                                "byte_stop": 681691,
                                "text": "I am authorized to state that Mr. Justice White has filed a dissenting opinion and is joined therein by Mr. Justice Douglas, Mr. Justice Brennan and Mr. Justice Powell."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
